long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Automatically transfer notes from Tandem Health to your medical record system.

This extension does not store any data, and is only used to transfer the notes.

Contact info@tandemhealth.ai to start using Tandem or get support with the usage of this plugin.
